text: Telefe Santa Fe (call sign LT 82 TV) is an Argentine broadcast television station on channel 13 owned by Telefe in Santa Fe, Argentina. The channel covers central and northwestern Santa Fe Province. It is operated by Paramount Global through the Telefe Group. ==Schedule== Currently, part of the channel's programming consists of retransmitting the contents of Channel 11 of Buenos Aires (head of the Telefe chain). ==Local programming== *Telefe Noticias Santa Fe - news *Sembrando ("Seeding") - country news *Martín Bustamante - country news *Nuestra Casa ("Our Home") - DIY and cooking *Otra Visión ("Another View") - health advice *Pausa en Familia ("Family Break") - religious == References == == Other websites == * * Telefe Interior Category:1966 establishments in South America Category:1960s establishments in Argentina Category:Telefe Category:Santa Fe, Argentina Category:Television channels in South America
